{
  "texts": [
    "As for deepfakes, it can be concluded that, even being a neutral technology, malicious applications can be very harmful and disruptive in society.",
    "Therefore, techniques advocated for prevention, detection and detention of spreading are essential, where huge coordinated efforts from research community, governments and private institutions should be promoted.",
    "Moreover, the detection of digital deception content is not enough, due to the fast development on the generation side.",
    "Therefore, further research has to be carried out regarding authentication.",
    "Guaranteeing a trusted content origin source in combination with a tracked history of it are powerful tools to combat online fake content."
  ]
}